OL,3,CBadenoch backs shadow justice
OL,4,Csecretary after Muslim comments
OL,6,FKemi Badenoch has told ITV News she
OL,7,F"stands by" her shadow justice
OL,8,Fsecretary, after his controversial
OL,9,Fcomments about Muslims.
OL,11,FSpeaking to ITV News' Harry Horton on
OL,12,FThursday, the leader of the opposition
OL,13,Fsaid the conservative MP Nick Timothy
OL,14,Fwas being attacked "for giving an
OL,15,Fopinion", after he sparked widespread
OL,16,Fcriticism for describing a mass Muslim
OL,17,Fpublic prayer as an "act of domination
OL,18,Fand division".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
