OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1774012289
OL,3,CBadenoch backs shadow justice
OL,4,Csecretary after Muslim comments
OL,6,F"I am sick and tired of people trying
OL,7,Fto shut everyone down when they have a
OL,8,Fdifferent opinion," she said during an
OL,9,Finterview at the Conservatives' local
OL,10,Felection launch on Thursday.
OL,12,F"It is because of that many people
OL,13,Fdon't say that something when they can
OL,14,Fsee something is wrong."
OL,16,FThe prime minister has urged Badenoch
OL,17,Fto sack her shadow justice secretary -
OL,18,Fbranding his comments "utterly
OL,19,Fappalling".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
