CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1774012289
OL,3,CBadenoch backs shadow justice
OL,4,Csecretary after Muslim comments
OL,6,FOn Monday, Timothy shared a clip of
OL,7,FLondon Mayor Sadiq Khan and other
OL,8,FMuslims praying at an open iftar event
OL,9,Fin Trafalgar Square, writing: "Too
OL,10,Fmany are too polite to say this. But
OL,11,Fmass ritual prayer in public places is
OL,12,Fan act of domination."
OL,14,FHe went on to say: "The domination of
OL,15,Fpublic places is straight from the
OL,16,FIslamist playbook."
OL,18,FOn Wednesday, Sir Keir Starmer called
OL,19,Fon Badenoch to sack Timothy, claiming
OL,20,Fthe Conservative Party "has a problem
OL,21,Fwith Muslims".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
