OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1774012289
OL,3,CBadenoch backs shadow justice
OL,4,Csecretary after Muslim comments
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,F"He said last night that Muslims
OL,12,Fpraying in public, including the mayor
OL,13,Fof London practising his faith, are
OL,14,Fnot welcome," Starmer said at Prime
OL,15,FMinister's Questions.
OL,17,F"If he were in my team, he would be
OL,18,Fgone. She should denounce his comments
OL,19,Fand she should sack him."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
