OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1774012289
OL,3,CBadenoch backs shadow justice
OL,4,Csecretary after Muslim comments
OL,6,FTimothy, a former special adviser to
OL,7,FTheresa May, was appointed by Badenoch
OL,8,Fin January.
OL,10,FHe has since doubled down on his
OL,11,Fcomments, saying on Thursday that he
OL,12,F"will not be silenced."
OL,14,F"Labour are only demonstrating that
OL,15,Fthey cannot see right from wrong," he
OL,16,Fwrote. "They will not stand up for our
OL,17,Fway of life. But we will," Timothy
OL,18,Fwrote on X.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
