CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1774012289
OL,3,CBadenoch backs shadow justice
OL,4,Csecretary after Muslim comments
OL,6,FKhan told La Repubblica he was
OL,7,F"heartbroken" and "angry" over the
OL,8,Ftweet, adding that he can "understand
OL,9,Fwhy many British Muslims are scared by
OL,10,Fsomebody who is so senior, who wants
OL,11,Fto be Lord Chancellor, saying what he
OL,12,Fsaid."
OL,14,F"But worryingly, his leader, somebody
OL,15,Fwho wants to be the prime minister,
OL,16,FKemi Badenoch, thinks it is British
OL,17,Fvalues to single out Muslims. It is
OL,18,FBritish values to respect each other,"
OL,19,Fhe added.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/6
